Package PDFjet.NET

Class CheckBox

  • Object
    • PDFjet.NET.CheckBox
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDrawable
    public class CheckBox
extends Object
implements IDrawable
    Creates a CheckBox, which can be set Checked or unChecked. By default the Check box is unChecked.
